origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
[['FinanceResearch.find_literature', {'name': 'FinanceResearch.find_literature', 'description': 'This function searches for academic literature on a specific topic.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of interest for the literature search.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'literature', 'description': 'A list of up to three relevant academic papers.'}]}], ['FinanceResearch.get_case_studies', {'name': 'FinanceResearch.get_case_studies', 'description': 'This function retrieves case studies related to a phenomenon in a specific market.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'market', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The market where the phenomenon is observed.'}, {'name': 'phenomenon', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The phenomenon of interest for case studies.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'case_studies', 'description': 'A list of up to three case studies related to the phenomenon in the market.'}]}], ['FinanceResearch.analyze_mechanism', {'name': 'FinanceResearch.analyze_mechanism', 'description': 'This function analyzes the mechanism behind a specific effect in a given context.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'effect', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The effect to analyze.'}, {'name': 'context', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The context in which the effect is observed.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis', 'description': 'A detailed analysis of the mechanism behind the effect in the context.'}]}], ['FinanceResearch.develop_strategies', {'name': 'FinanceResearch.develop_strategies', 'description': 'This function develops strategies to address a specific effect in a market.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'effect', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The effect to develop strategies for.'}, {'name': 'market', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The market where the effect is observed.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'strategies', 'description': 'A list of strategies to address the effect in the market.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `FinanceResearch.find_literature` 并传入 `topic`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "FinanceResearch.find_literature",
    "args": "{'topic': '羊群效应'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
